<script setup lang="ts">import { reactive, computed, getCurrentInstance, ref } from 'vue'
import { usePinceauRuntime } from 'pinceau/runtime'

import type { PropType } from 'vue'

type HTMLElementsTags = keyof HTMLElementTagNameMap

const __$pProps = defineProps({
  as: {
    type: String as PropType<HTMLElementsTags>,
    required: false,
    default: 'div'
  },

  ...{"padded":{"required":false as const,"type":[Boolean, Object] as import('vue').PropType<boolean | { [key in import('pinceau').PinceauMediaQueries]?: boolean }>,"default":true as const},"fluid":{"required":false as const,"type":[Boolean, Object] as import('vue').PropType<boolean | { [key in import('pinceau').PinceauMediaQueries]?: boolean }>,"default":false as const}}
})
const __$pVariants = {"padded":{"true":{"px":"{elements.container.padding.mobile}","@xs":{"px":"{elements.container.padding.xs}"},"@sm":{"px":"{elements.container.padding.sm}"},"@md":{"px":"{elements.container.padding.md}"}}},"fluid":{"true":{},"false":{"maxWidth":"{elements.container.maxWidth}"}}}

const { $pinceau } = usePinceauRuntime(__$pProps, __$pVariants, undefined)
</script>

<template>
  <component :is="as" class="container" :class="[$pinceau]">
    <slot />
  </component>
</template>

<style lang="postcss" transformed scoped>
.container{margin-inline-start:auto;margin-inline-end:auto;width:100%;}
</style>
